        "content": "Plaintiff DeShawn Carter brings this action under 42 U.S.C. § 1983 against City of Riverside, Officer Kevin Walsh, and Officer Maria Chen for violations of the Fourth and Fourteenth Amendments arising from a traffic stop on October 4, 2025, during which Plaintiff alleges he was subjected to excessive force, unlawful detention, and racially selective enforcement. Plaintiff seeks compensatory and punitive damages, declaratory relief, and an injunction requiring policy and training reforms."
